{"id":226251,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":5,"day":15}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"人民科学","column":"","genre":"","count":"152","ytitle":"","mtitle":"小智慧2×2=5","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘一二如二；二二如四；二三如六；……’是我们背得烂熟的‘九九歌诀’。但有一位要数学戏法的人，却变出‘二二如五’来。不信，请看下面:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这当然是个毫无疑问的等式了:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"16-36=25-45"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两边加上同等的数字当然还是相等:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515f070801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>两边配平方，成:</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515f070802.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>亦即:</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515f070803.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>两边开方:</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515f070804.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>岂不是2×2=5么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你晓得:关键是在那里么?</FONT>"}]}